Scheduler (Cron Job) 
• Add amit user and set password “test” 
• After 2 minutes login mode 
• After 4 minutes no login mode

Solution:- 
- crontab -e 
    - Starting from min Hours-time(am/pm) date month week  /usr/ sbin/useradd amit
    - 51  22-24 15 11 * /usr/sbin/useradd -u amit11
    - */1  22-24 15 11 * /usr/bin/echo "test"|passwd amit11 --stdin
    - */2  22-24 15 11 * /usr/sbin/usermod -U amit11
    - */2  22-24 15 11 * /usr/sbin/usermod -L amit11

